MAIN_MESSAGE: This is a message for customers in the TD9 postcode area of Newcastleton. It is necessary for our engineers to carry out an emergency shutdown at 11:05pm following reports of a tree on an overhead line at Leahaugh Farm and this may affect the supply to your property. We will work to get your power back on as quickly and as safely as possible by 1:15am. We will update this message if this information changes. We apologise for the inconvenience and thank you for your patience. This message was updated at 11:08 PM on Tuesday, 17 November 2020.
